@startuml BE1_Logins_StateChart
hide empty description

[*] --> displayLoginPage
displayLoginPage : display login screen

displayLoginPage --> verifyCredentials : credentials entered
verifyCredentials : verify credentials

verifyCredentials --> loginError : invalid credentials
loginError : display error message
loginError --> displayLoginPage : retry

verifyCredentials --> classifyRole : valid credentials
classifyRole : classify user role

classifyRole --> requestAdditionalAuthentication : role has additional permissions
requestAdditionalAuthentication : request extra authentication
requestAdditionalAuthentication --> loginError : verification failed
requestAdditionalAuthentication --> grantAccess : verification succeeded

classifyRole --> grantAccess : standard role
grantAccess : grant access based on RBAC permissions

grantAccess --> redirectDashboard
redirectDashboard : redirect to correct dashboard

redirectDashboard --> recordLoginEvent
recordLoginEvent : record login event in audit logs

recordLoginEvent --> [*]
@enduml